        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/eu-uk-increase-sudan-aid-london-conference.png" alt="EU and Britain boost aid for Sudan at London conference" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
